metadata.name: It takes two to Tango
metadata.description:
Tango is like fire full of passion and sparks. 
Like fire which needs an oxygen to burn, Tango needs passionate and fiery partners to live its full potential.

Like fire it is a living growing constantly changing organism. 
Like fire it depends on it's partner. 
Like fire it dies if there is no spark. 

This piece is the first in many in the collection "Foundation on fire" where I'll be playing and experimenting with fire and digital effects.

NFT properties:
Size: 2164 x 3500 px I 300dpi I png I 24 bit RGB
by @Uzzy - June 2023
